id: 2629
name: Victory Auctions
power: 1.0
text: |
  The Treasuror CAN conduct a Victory Auction if no other Victory
  Auction is ongoing. The Treasuror MUST do so at least once a
  month, and SHOULD do so at least twice each month.

  A Victory Auction includes the following lots:

  * one new Win Card.

  The currency of a Victory Auction is coins (minimum bid 1).
